snippet: Paul Casey and Webb Simpson shot matching 62s for a share of the lead at eight under par in the first round of the Sony Open in Honolulu.
abstract: Paul Casey and Webb Simpson share lead at Sony Open in Honolulu with eight under par; other golf news noted.

byline.original: By REUTERS and THE ASSOCIATED PRESS

lead_paragraph: Paul Casey and Webb Simpson shot matching 62s for a share of the lead at eight under par in the first round of the Sony Open in Honolulu.

headline.main: Casey and Simpson Share Lead in Sony Open
